On completion they transition to the \"eat wait\" (ground) or \"eat fall\" (air) states where Kirby holds the opponent in his stomach.\n\n**Copied Sheik neutral B input** — `ftKb_SkSpecialNLoop_IASA` and `ftKb_SkSpecialAirNLoop_IASA` handle input checks during Kirby's copied Sheik Needle Storm loop. If B is released, Kirby fires the needles and transitions to the end state; if a shoulder button is pressed, the move is cancelled.\n\n**Copied Mewtwo neutral B** — `ftKb_SpecialNMt_80107568` enters Kirby's copied Mewtwo Shadow Ball charge, initializing the motion state and charge variables.\n\n**Hat model loading** — `ftKb_SpecialN_800EF35C` is part of the pipeline that loads the 3D hat model onto Kirby's head after copying a character's ability.\n\n**Copied Jigglypuff neutral B** — `ftKb_PrSpecialAirNStart_Anim` handles the aerial startup animation for Kirby's copied Jigglypuff Rollout.\n\n## Verification\n- All 7 functions 100% match (verified by overnight script)\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/claude-code)","created_at":"2026-03-21T15:02:20Z","updated_at":"2026-05-14T01:34:29Z","closed_at":"2026-03-21T20:41:25Z","merged_at":"2026-03-21T20:41:25Z","merge_commit_sha":"56bac9793360876d5ad9fafa6c997eda2cfb88d4","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2343/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/2343/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/issues/2343/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doldecomp/melee/statuses/b10dd7bf9c8b3f8d530533c074632d68d5a2b48a","head":{"label":"johnwinston:pr/decomp-kirby-2","ref":"pr/decomp-kirby-2","sha":"b10dd7bf9c8b3f8d530533c074632d68d5a2b48a","user":{"login":"johnwinston","id":18341794,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE4MzQ